{"tid":2083974,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"本民前算唔算騎劫咗場運動","createTime":"2020-06-29T05:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T17:29:39.000Z","uid":61348,"like":4,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"50c69d61662f93e0906410a2afce51544bd2b5a2","tid":2083974,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"無出現過場運動 人哋叫口你口號就當場運動係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家先知道點解連登仔要人叫光復香港時代革命 原來就係想場騎劫場運動 幫梁天琦造神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂大佬你班本民粉連登叫人叫口號 唔通潑冷水叫你唔好叫咩 你唔好當叫啲人就要支持你先得架<br />\n<br />\n講到咩無魚蛋 無本土 咁無熱狗係咪無本民前喇係咪呀 無陳雲係咪無本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家啲人勇武關梁天琦咩事 又想拎功勞當自己<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦只係關魚蛋事 魚蛋無錯佢有功勞 但就係咁多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n造神黨好撚嘔心 你哋越造神其他人只會越反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082fe2540ac7de91089d95680e25caabddd018d6","tid":2083974,"uid":177213,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akqrMs5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakqrMs5.png&h=a62dbfd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KWq11r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KWq11r.png&h=06320806&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"889af5759d094345518a8aa406da1965e8b608a1","tid":2083974,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>71 維園見</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"82b641968912cb6cb6f95243dcfd913faf3920ea","tid":2083974,"uid":38563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"無討論價值，拉"},{"p